additionalProperty.value: Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. Consult your doctor before use, if you are taking medication. Seek medical advice for use under 18 years. Ask your healthcare professional before use if you are pregnant or breastfeeding. Do not accept if tamper evident seal is broken or missing. Keep out of reach of children. description: Caltrate VITAMIN D DAILY helps to ensure optimal calcium absorption, improving bone density and strength in those with low vitamin D levels. Vitamin D has also been shown to help improve muscle strength and balance therefore reducing the risk of falls and subsequent fractures.
